(1, 'PESMP35', '2024-04-24 09:31:20', b'0', '<div class=\"product-description-container\">\n<h4 class=\"product-description-heading\">About This Product</h4>\n<div class=\"rte rte--spread-out product-description read-mode\">\n<p>PreSonus&reg; Eris&reg;-series studio monitors are used worldwide by audio engineers and producers who need to hear every detail of their recordings. PreSonus best-selling studio monitors just got better! Eris 3.5 media reference monitors deliver studio-quality sound in an elegant, compact form factor that makes them ideally suited for bedroom studios, video production, and high-fidelity gaming setups.</p>\n<p>Features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>3.5-inch, woven-composite, low-frequency driver</li>\n<li>1-inch, ultra-low mass, silk-dome, high-frequency driver</li>\n<li>50W, Class AB dual amplification</li>\n<li>80 Hz to 20 kHz frequency response</li>\n<li>98 dB SPL (Peak, @ 1 meter)</li>\n<li>High- and low-frequency Acoustic Tuning controls</li>\n<li>Balanced, &frac14;-inch TRS inputs; unbalanced, ⅛-inch stereo and RCA inputs; and integrated stereo headphone amplifier with front-panel ⅛-inch output</li>\n<li>Protection: RF interference, output-current limiting, over-temperature, turn-on/off transient, subsonic filter</li>\n<li>Power Saver mode (engages after 40 minutes)</li>\n<li>Comes with speaker wire, ⅛-inch TRS to stereo RCA cable, and stereo ⅛-inch TRS to ⅛-inch TRS cable</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"product-specifications-container\">\n<p class=\"anchor-target\" data-value=\"specifications\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 class=\"product-description-heading product-description__sub-header\">Th&ocirc;ng tin chi tiết</h4>\n<table class=\"product-description__specs unstriped\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Wattage</td>\n<td>25W (Each)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Cabinet Material</td>\n<td>Vinyl-laminated, Medium-Density Fiberboard</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Protections</td>\n<td>RF interference, Output-current limiting, Over-temperature, Turn-on/off transient, Subsonic filter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Controls</td>\n<td>Volume, High Frequency (&plusmn;6 dB, centre 10 kHz, continuously variable), Low Frequency (&plusmn;6 dB, centre 100 Hz, continuously variable)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Peak SPL</td>\n<td>98 dB (@ 1 meter)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Crossover</td>\n<td>2.8 kHz</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Inputs</td>\n<td>1 x Stereo 1/8\", 2 x Balanced 1/4&rdquo; TRS, 2 x Unbalanced RCA</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Transducers</td>\n<td>1&rdquo; Ultra Low Mass, Silk Dome Tweeter (HF), 3.5\" Woven Composite (LF)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Frequency Response</td>\n<td>80 Hz - 20 kHz</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Impedance</td>\n<td>10 k&Omega;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Includes</td>\n<td>One Pair - PreSonus Eris Media Reference Monitors, One - 1.5M 1/8&rdquo; TRS to 2x RCA cable, One - 1.5M 1/8&rdquo; TRS stereo cable, One - 2M bare-wire speaker cable, Eight - Foam Feet, Quick Start Guide, IEC Power Cable</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Dimensions</td>\n<td>5.53\" (W) x 6.46\" (D) x 8.27\" (H)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Weight</td>\n<td>3.1 kg / 6.83 lbs</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>', 'http://res.cloudinary.com/dxqh3xpza/image/upload/v1713925803/y8acpvmc2ql1ppz9bsfw.webp', 'PreSonus Eris 3.5 Studio Monitor, Pair', 319000, 30, 0, 1),
(2, 'MJ100TG', '2024-04-24 09:35:28', b'0', '<h4 class=\"product-description-heading\">About This Product</h4>\n<div class=\"rte rte--spread-out product-description read-mode\">\n<p>The British-built 100 Watt JVM210H head offers a more straightforward two channel preamp (Clean/Crunch and Overdrive) than the JVM410H four channels, for guitarists who prefer a more stripped down ?fewer frills? approach. The two independent channels both have three modes. Each mode reconfigures the gain structure of each channel, making six modes in total that can take you from ?Plexi?/JTM45 cleans through JCM800 punch to modern high-gain tones.</p>\n<p>The JVM210H is equipped with the same groundbreaking technology as its big brother, the JVM410H. Featuring two studio quality Reverbs (one per channel), with individual channel EQ, two Master Volumes, and a memory that will recall your Reverb, FX Loop and Master settings.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Model:</strong>&nbsp;JVM210H</li>\n<li><strong>Type:</strong> Tube</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'http://res.cloudinary.com/dxqh3xpza/image/upload/v1713926050/lwjpsucxjp5hfrgz55da.webp', 'Marshall JVM210H 100W Tube Guitar Amplifier Head', 4700000, 50, 0, 1),
(3, 'FLMAGAUK230', '2024-04-24 09:37:14', b'0', '<div class=\"product-description-container\">\n<h4 class=\"product-description-heading\">About This Product</h4>\n<div class=\"rte rte--spread-out product-description\">\n<p>Loudbox Micro packs 40 watts of clean acoustic power into a lunchbox-sized acoustic combo. A sealed cabinet design paired with a bi-amplified driver configuration generates rich, full tones from your acoustic instruments. It features a dedicated microphone channel plus an instrument channel with Fishman&rsquo;s legendary preamp and tone control design.</p>\n<p>Use the high-quality digital reverb and chorus on the instrument channel to create space and textures while the reverb is there - ready on the microphone channel. Loudbox Micro also includes an aux input, a balanced XLR D.I. output, and a headphone jack when you want to play quietly.</p>\n<p>With Loudbox Micro, aspiring acoustic musicians are finally able to experience the dynamics and quality of sound of more expensive Loudbox models in an easy-to-use amp that&rsquo;s inspiring to practice and record with.https://youtu.be/gjkg9TPGE00</p>\n<p>Features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>40 Watts with Master Volume</li>\n<li>Two channels: Instrument &amp; Microphone</li>\n<li>Digital Reverb &amp; Chorus</li>\n<li>1/8&rdquo; Auxiliary Input</li>\n<li>Balanced XLR D.I. Output</li>\n<li>3.5mm Headphone Output</li>\n<li>1/4&rdquo; input for active or passive pickups</li>\n<li>Feedback-fighting Phase switch</li>\n<li>3-band EQ: low, mid, high tone controls</li>\n<li>Reverb level</li>\n<li>Dual-function Chorus</li>\n<li>XLR input for dynamic microphones</li>\n<li>2-band EQ with low and high tone controls</li>\n<li>Reverb level</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"product-specifications-container\">\n<p class=\"anchor-target\" data-value=\"specifications\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 class=\"product-description-heading product-description__sub-header\">Th&ocirc;ng tin chi tiết</h4>\n<table class=\"product-description__specs unstriped\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Power</td>\n<td>40W, Bi-Amplified</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Channel</td>\n<td>Two: Instrument &amp; Microphone</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Drivers</td>\n<td>5.25\" Poly Cone Woofer, 0.8\" Soft Dome Tweeter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Effects</td>\n<td>Reverb and Dual-Function Chorus</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Aux Input</td>\n<td>3.5mm Input</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Outputs</td>\n<td>Balanced XLR D.I. Output, 3.5mm Headphone Output</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Dimensions</td>\n<td>.1&rdquo; (D) x 10.4&rdquo; (W) x 9.5&rdquo; (H) / 206mm (D) x 264mm (W) x 242mm (H)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Weight</td>\n<td>4.1 kg / 9.1 lbs</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>', 'http://res.cloudinary.com/dxqh3xpza/image/upload/v1713926153/psol5j1e02lfurkegxfe.webp', 'Fishman Loudbox Micro Acoustic Guitar Amplifier, UK, 230V', 9150000, 50, 0, 1),
(4, 'S40AGEPBG', '2024-04-24 09:39:33', b'0', '<div class=\"product-description-container\">\n<h4 class=\"product-description-heading\">About This Product</h4>\n<div class=\"rte rte--spread-out product-description\">\n<p>C&acirc;y Squier đầu ti&ecirc;n được ra mắt v&agrave;o năm 1982 v&agrave; l&agrave; kết quả mỹ m&atilde;n của qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh nghi&ecirc;n cứu c&ocirc;ng phu nhằm tạo n&ecirc;n thiết kế Fender&reg; ch&iacute;nh thống với mức gi&aacute; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng hợp l&yacute;. Bộ sưu tập Squier 40th Anniversary kỷ niệm h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh 40 năm của ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c guitar cho người mới bắt đầu của Fender với phi&ecirc;n bản Gold Edition v&agrave; Vintage Edition đặc biệt cho d&ograve;ng Telecaster&reg;, Stratocaster&reg;, Jazzmaster&reg;, Precision Bass&reg; v&agrave; Jazz Bass&reg;.</p>\n<p>Squier&reg; 40th Anniversary Precision Bass&reg;, Gold Edition l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản cực chất với nhiều đặc điểm hấp dẫn được n&acirc;ng cấp d&agrave;nh cho những tay guitar đam m&ecirc; Squier. Hardware mạ v&agrave;ng ấn tượng, pickguard bằng Aluminium anode v&agrave;ng gold, mặt cần cứng c&aacute;p bằng gỗ Indian laurel, inlays pearloid h&igrave;nh khối, neck plate c&oacute; khắc logo kỷ niệm được phủ finish b&oacute;ng bẩy, c&acirc;y P Bass&reg; n&agrave;y c&oacute; vẻ ngo&agrave;i thu h&uacute;t v&agrave; sẵn s&agrave;ng toả s&aacute;ng dưới &aacute;nh đ&egrave;n s&acirc;n khấu. Những tinh chỉnh hướng đến sự thoải m&aacute;i khi chơi nhạc cho guitarist gồm cần đ&agrave;n d&aacute;ng &ldquo;C&rdquo; mỏng, thoải m&aacute;i, lướt ng&oacute;n dễ d&agrave;ng, bộ kho&aacute; phong c&aacute;ch cổ điển, ngựa đ&agrave;n 4-saddle với barrel saddle đ&aacute;ng tin cậy, c&aacute;c pickup split single-coil do Fender thiết kế với c&aacute;c nam ch&acirc;m alnico 5 mang đến chất &acirc;m P Bass th&acirc;n thuộc.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"product-specifications-container\">\n<p class=\"anchor-target\" data-value=\"specifications\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 class=\"product-description-heading product-description__sub-header\">Th&ocirc;ng tin chi tiết</h4>\n<table class=\"product-description__specs unstriped\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>D&aacute;ng đ&agrave;n</td>\n<td>Precision Bass&reg;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gỗ th&acirc;n</td>\n<td>Nyatoh</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Finish th&acirc;n</td>\n<td>Gloss Polyurethane</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>D&aacute;ng cần</td>\n<td>\"C\" Shape</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Chất liệu mặt cần</td>\n<td>Indian Laurel</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Độ cong mặt cần</td>\n<td>9,5\" (241 mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Độ d&agrave;i Scale</td>\n<td>34\" (864 mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Số ph&iacute;m</td>\n<td>20 Narrow Tall Frets</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Inlays mặt cần</td>\n<td>Pearloid Block</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Pickups</td>\n<td>Fender&reg; Designed Alnico Split Single-Coil (Neck)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ngựa đ&agrave;n</td>\n<td>4-Saddle Vintage-Style</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Pickguard</td>\n<td>1-Ply Gold Anodized Aluminium</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>D&acirc;y đ&agrave;n</td>\n<td>Nickel Plated Steel (.045-.105 Gauges)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Bộ kho&aacute;</td>\n<td>Vintage-Style</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Hardware Finish</td>\n<td>Gold Plated</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>', 'http://res.cloudinary.com/dxqh3xpza/image/upload/v1713926295/rpupoarepph59zrpu46n.webp', 'Squier 40th Anniversary Gold Edition Precision Bass Guitar, Lake Placid Blue (B-Stock)', 1250000, 49, 1, 2),
(5, 'SCSEGMFB23', '2024-04-24 09:41:59', b'0', '<h4 class=\"product-description-heading\">About This Product</h4>\n<div class=\"rte rte--spread-out product-description\">\n<p>Starcaster đ&atilde; ph&aacute; vỡ khu&ocirc;n mẫu thiết kế đ&agrave;n guitar semi-hollow bằng kiểu th&acirc;n offset khi n&oacute; được tr&igrave;nh l&agrave;ng v&agrave;o những năm 70, Starcaster mang đến &acirc;m thanh linh hoạt v&agrave; kiểu d&aacute;ng độc lạ cho những người chơi ưa mạo hiểm nhất. Contemporary Active Starcaster l&agrave; một cuộc c&aacute;ch mạng của một mẫu Fender nguy&ecirc;n bản, được thiết kế với kiểu th&acirc;n semi-hollow giảm thiểu feedback tới mức tối đa v&agrave; được nạp năng lượng bởi pickups humbucking k&eacute;p active ceramic Squier SQR cho &acirc;m thanh high-output. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh năng th&acirc;n thiện với người chơi bao gồm cần đ&agrave;n kiểu &ldquo;C&rdquo; mỏng, thoải m&aacute;i với độ cong cần 12&rdquo; gi&uacute;p lướt ng&oacute;n nhanh c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c ph&iacute;m đ&agrave;n narrow-tall, cũng như stop tailpeice gi&uacute;p tuning ổn định. Mẫu Squier n&agrave;y cũng c&oacute; đường viền headstock được sơn đồng bộ, hardware mạ chrome m&agrave;u đen v&agrave; finish cần đ&agrave;n bằng satin mượt m&agrave; cho cảm nhận tự nhi&ecirc;n. &nbsp;</p>\n<p>Th&ocirc;ng tin chi tiết: &nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Kiểu th&acirc;n: Starcaster&reg; &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Gỗ th&acirc;n: Laminated Maple &nbsp;</li>\n<li>M&agrave;u th&acirc;n: Flat Black&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Finish th&acirc;n: Matte Urethane&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Chất liệu mặt cần: Maple &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Độ cong cần: 12\" (305 mm) &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Độ d&agrave;i scale: 25,5&rdquo; (648 mm) &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Số ph&iacute;m: 22 &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Inlays mặt cần: Black Dot &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Pickup(s): Squier&reg; SQR&trade; Ceramic Humbucker (Bridge &amp; Neck) &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Ngựa đ&agrave;n: Adjusto-Matic&trade; with Anchored Tailpiece &nbsp;</li>\n<li>D&acirc;y đ&agrave;n: Nickel Plated Steel (.009-.042 Gauges) &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Bộ kho&aacute;: Die-Cast Sealed &nbsp;</li>\n<li>Hardware Finish: Black Chrome</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'http://res.cloudinary.com/dxqh3xpza/image/upload/v1713926441/ljqp4xz127nptrfowdyb.webp', 'Squier Contemporary Starcaster Electric Guitar, Maple FB, Flat Black (B-Stock)', 968000, 447, 3, 2);

